profile.description: This profile defines the domain specific UML dialect for the IVOA data modelling efforts.

package.name: IVOAValueTypes
package.description:
UML DataType is the base class of Primitive Type and Enumeration.
This types are generic and does not represent specific implementation types.
Primitive type is a predefined datatype which does not have a structure.
ivoaIdentifier is a DataType since it has possibly a structure.

PUBLIC users can be seen by others who may want to invite them to groups. PRIVATE users do not want to be invited. Usewrs will be able to switch their own visibility between PUBLIS and PRIVATE only.
